webpackJsonp([17916839802491],{8399:function(e,t){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Bloglines Down",date:"16 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-16-bloglines-down/",tags:"Y2005"},html:'<p>I can\'t log in to my Bloglines accounts this morning... and it seems like <a title="Technorati: Search for bloglines" href="http://www.technorati.com/cosmos/search.html?rank=&url=bloglines">noone else can either</a>. </p>\n<p>Of course, if you depend on Bloglines to manage your reading, you\'ll never read this.</p>\n<p><strong>Update:</strong> As of 16:15 CET, it seems to be back.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Sixty Years After Bergen-Belsen",date:"15 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-15-sixty-years-after-bergenbelsen/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Double Feature",date:"19 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-19-double-feature/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Sixty Years After Bergen-Belsen",date:"15 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-15-sixty-years-after-bergenbelsen/",tags:"Y2005"},html:'<p><a href="http://medienkritik.typepad.com/blog/2005/04/this_day_in_his.html">David\'s Medienkritik</a> reminded me that this is the 60th anniversary of the liberation of <a href="http://www.bergen-belsen.de/en/">Bergen-Belsen</a>, located about 50 km from our house. I\'ve <a href="http://www.papascott.de/archives/2002/04/11/explaining-the-unexplainable/" title="PapaScott: Explaining the Unexplainable">mentioned before</a> that Bergen-Belsen is perhaps the eeriest place I\'ve ever been. There are no original buildings from the camp. They were all burned, and there are no replicas. There is a small museum, and various memorials, but most of the grounds consist of heather-covered mounds. Dozens of mounds. Each is a mass grave representing thousands of dead.  The stillness is overwhelming.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"29560 Unread",date:"14 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-14-29560-unread/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Bloglines Down",date:"16 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-16-bloglines-down/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"29560 Unread",date:"14 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-14-29560-unread/",tags:"Y2005"},html:"<p>I really should check my spam folder more often than every six months...</p>"},next:{fields:{title:"Blue Train",date:"11 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-11-blue-train/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Sixty Years After Bergen-Belsen",date:"15 Apr 2005",slug:"/2005-04-15-sixty-years-after-bergenbelsen/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:323,pageCount:1101}}}});
